  "description": "<p>When it comes to staying warm while camping, you need a sleeping bag that can deliver. By laminating insulation to the shell, this unique construction eliminates cold spots and maximizes the loft of your insulation. Plus, the thermally mapped insulation ensures you get the most warmth where you need it most.</p><ul><li>Shell is lightweight ripstop nylon, lining is soft woven nylon</li><li>DWR finish on the shell protects your bag from tent wall condensation and makes it easier to keep your bag clean</li><li>Thermal.Q insulation is made with 80% recycled fibres and performs well when damp</li><li>Horizontal baffles prevent the insulation from shifting and creating cold spots</li><li>Hood lets you lift and move your head, even when fully zipped up and has a one-handed cinch adjustment</li><li>Draft collar prevents warm air from escaping</li><li>Contoured footbox feels natural and roomy</li><li>Includes a mesh storage bag and a nylon compression sack</li></ul>",
